json.text: This is Nehza. The protector, the quick.
A deceivingly playful façade conceals his immense power.
Nehza’s abilities keep his enemies at bay and his allies renewed.
Fire Walker leaves a trail of flames at his feet as he runs
dealing fire damage to enemies that come in contact
while also increasing his movement speed.
Blazing Chakram throws a fire chakram;
if it hits an enemy, they will become marked.
Enemies who die while marked emit a healing pulse to Nehza’s allies within a small radius.
Triggering this ability while the chakram is in flight will cause Nehza to teleport to it.
Warding Halo creates a protective ring of fire around Nehza
that absorbs incoming damage while also hurting enemies who venture too close to the ring.
Watch your step Tenno. Divine Spears impales enemies in a radius around Nehza, pinning them to the spears.
When deactivated, they retract, slamming enemies into the ground with incredible force.
Nehza’s abilities are easily modded to increase their effectiveness.
Adding strength and ranged mods will positively impact all of Nehza’s powers—
and adding a duration mod benefits all but Warding Halo.
Feel the heat, Tenno. Nehza is a burning thing, and he makes a fiery ring.
